terrapeer.vui.j3dui.utils
Class Assert

java.lang.Object
  terrapeer.vui.j3dui.utils.Assert
public class Assert
extends java.lang.Object

Static methods that provide support for "assertions". The default is for assertions to be enabled. Use setEnabled() or useProperty???() with command line properties to explicitly enable and disable it. All output is printed to System.err.
